verbose_text: Treatment with 1 muM Icaritin upregulated osteocalcin, RUNX family transcription factor 2, tissue-nonspecific alkaline phosphatase and beta-catenin, and suppressed sclerostin (SOST) gene expression in different stages of osteogenic differentiation.
